name: Barong boi
description:
Joining the #hendonesia bandwagon, here comes:

Barong Boi is a young man who used to be afraid of the Barong mask, but on the other hand he is also curious and likes the details of the mask.

He wants this Barong mask to be known by many people without scaring children (like he was). That's why he made a barong mask with a modified version to make it cuter. He uses it together with clothes that are common in society to easily spread how cool the Barong mask really is.
